text: William Abdy is the name of: *Sir William Abdy, 4th Baronet (1689–1750), English landowner *Sir William Abdy, 6th Baronet (ca. 1732–1803), Royal Navy officer *Sir William Abdy, 7th Baronet (1779–1868), English landowner and Member of Parliament for Malmesbury *Sir William Abdy, 2nd Baronet (1844–1910) ==See also== *Abdy baronets
title: William Abdy
